<subsection><title>Wrap-Up</title>
<p>In this Lesson, we worked on the following skills and goals related to logarithms:</p>
<p><ul>
<li><p>Use the properties of logarithms to simplify expressions</p></li>
<li><p>Avoid mistakes using the properties of logarithms.</p></li>    
<li><p>Solve exponential equations using base 10 logarithms</p></li>    
 </ul></p>

